Command - Annotation Type in fr.alex6.discord.cmx
A method annotation to register a command inside a CommandModule class, this annotation takes the following arguments - value: command name - aliases: command aliases default {} - executionRule: define if a command can be executed in private and/or text channel default ExecutionRule.TEXT_CHANNEL
